# Digital Talent Management System – Low-Fidelity Wireframes

## 📌 Overview
This project showcases low-fidelity wireframes for a Digital Talent Management System.  
The focus is on designing the core authentication flows to ensure a smooth and secure user experience.

These wireframes were created using Figma and emphasize structure, layout, and user flow rather than visual design.

---

## 🎯 Features

### 🔐 Login
- Input fields:
  - Email / Username
  - Password
- Actions:
  - Login button
  - Navigate to Sign Up
  - Forgot Password link

---

### 📝 Sign Up
- Input fields:
  - Full Name
  - Email Address
  - Password
  - Confirm Password
- Action:
  - Create Account button
- Redirects to Login after successful registration

---

### 🔁 Forgot Password (Request Reset)
- Input:
  - Registered Email Address
- Action:
  - Send Verification Code

---

### 🔢 Forgot Password (Verify Code)
- Input:
  - OTP / Verification Code
- Action:
  - Verify Code
- Handles invalid or expired codes

---

### 🔑 Forgot Password (Set New Password)
- Input fields:
  - New Password
  - Confirm Password
- Action:
  - Reset Password
- Redirects to Login after successful reset

---

## 🧠 Design Approach
- Low-fidelity (Lo-Fi) wireframes
- Focus on:
  - User flow
  - Layout structure
  - Navigation clarity
- Minimal styling (grayscale, placeholders)

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Figma

